{
  "_doc": "掃描清單（進版控、受審）。scan.sh 引擎讀 entries：有 args 者引擎執行（動詞限唯讀白名單，並依 api 對 services-enabled.json 做啟用預檢——空回應時 API 未啟用則改判資料缺口，防 Dataflow 型『未啟用仍回 []』的相反結論）；handledIn=scan.sh 者引擎不執行（該掃描仍由 scan.sh 程式碼負責，通常因為與 describe 迴圈耦合或有結構性例外行為），此處只『宣告覆蓋的 assetTypes』。coverage-check.sh 的 COVERED = 所有 entries 的 assetTypes 聯集（單一來源）。args 不含 --project，引擎自動附加 --project <id>。新增標準服務：加一筆 args 條目即可（你自己就能做）；行為不標準（多 region 合併、describe 迴圈、stderr 污染、回應非 []）者用 handledIn 並在 scan.sh 寫程式碼。",
  "entries": [
    { "section": "global", "out": "global/iam-custom-roles", "api": "iam.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["iam","roles","list"], "assetTypes": ["iam.googleapis.com/Role"] },
    { "section": "global", "out": "global/org-policies", "api": "cloudresourcemanager.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["resource-manager","org-policies","list"], "assetTypes": [],
      "note": "走 Resource Manager API（一直啟用），不依賴 orgpolicy.googleapis.com；空＝未設定（有效證據），故 api 設 cloudresourcemanager 讓預檢不誤判" },
    { "section": "global", "out": "global/api-keys", "api": "apikeys.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["services","api-keys","list"], "assetTypes": ["apikeys.googleapis.com/Key"] },

    { "section": "network", "out": "network/networks", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","networks","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Network"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/subnets", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","networks","subnets","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Subnetwork"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/routes", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","routes","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Route"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/firewall-rules", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","firewall-rules","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Firewall"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/addresses", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","addresses","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Address"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/routers", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","routers","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Router"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/vpn-tunnels", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","vpn-tunnels","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/VpnTunnel"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/vpn-gateways", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","vpn-gateways","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/VpnGateway"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/interconnects", "api": "compute.googleapis.com",
      "args": ["compute","interconnects","list"], "assetTypes": ["compute.googleapis.com/Interconnect"] },
    { "section": "network", "out": "network/vpc-connectors", "api": "vpcaccess.googleapis.com",
